==================== Context Pilot — IT delivery sheet ====================

  Unit            : {{ inventory_hostname }}
  Maintenance URL : https://{{ ansible_host | default(inventory_hostname) }}:9090
  Admin email     : {{ cp_seed_admin_email }}
  Admin password  : {{ cp_seed_admin_password }}

  This password is UNIQUE to this unit and is NOT stored anywhere else.
  Keep this sheet physically secure; shred it once setup is complete.

  First-time setup (over the LAN):
    1. Open the maintenance console at the URL above.
       (A browser TLS warning is expected — the box uses a private CA.)
    2. Sign in with the email + password above; change the password
       (and set a real admin email) when prompted.
    3. Give the box a name / IP; download the CA root and push it to your
       clients (GPO/MDM), verifying the displayed fingerprint.
    4. Click "Finalize" — the cockpit comes up on https://<name>.

